ticipate human trafficking's future, and then we are better able to fight it.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 4aAntiquity. 4aEarly Modern Studies. 4aHigh Middle Ages. 4aHistory, Art History, and Archaeology. 4aMedieval Studies. 4aSociology and Social History. 70(DE-588)4003677-70(DE-627)1063888430(DE-576)208852492aAusbeutung2gnd 70(DE-588)4125897-60(DE-627)1046651490(DE-576)20958050XaMenschenhandel2gnd 70(DE-588)4129108-60(DE-627)1045354740(DE-576)209607793aMittelalter2gnd 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aslavery, slave trade, prostitution, sex trafficking, medieval history, Middle Ages.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068955608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP ROW Ebook Package English 2020z978311069630140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048551552zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048551552423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048551552/original  a978-3-11-068955-6  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  a978-3-11-069630-1  PP ROW Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070473-0  